      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to a standard that transcends the typical secondary market offering. This vehicle remains in a state of aesthetic and mechanical preservation that rivals its original showroom delivery. Every detail, from the pristine interior surfaces to the flawless exterior finish, has been curated for the most discerning enthusiast. This is an acquisition for those who demand uncompromising quality and an unrivaled driving experience.",
