      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in such incredible shape, it\u2019s like it just left the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014spotless inside and out, and it drives perfectly. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand new price tag, this is the one! I've taken such good care of it and I'm sure you're going to love it. Can't wait for it to find a great new home!",
