      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered icon, maintained to a concourse standard. The 3.2L longitudinal inline-six features high-pressure VANOS and individual throttle bodies, providing an uncompromising 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory variable M differential lock. This chassis is mechanically pristine, featuring professional rear subframe reinforcement and documented rod bearing replacement. Finished in Carbon Black, the vehicle retains its factory-spec suspension geometry with no bushing deflection or hydraulic weeping. An unmodified, investment-grade specimen for the purist collector.",
